I have to be completely honest at this
tire is at the moment, I don't think I

00:04:43.440 --> 00:04:47.610
could ride home on it, but I can feel I've
been riding along the bits where I've got

00:04:47.610 --> 00:04:50.790
that folded over pieces of grass
in there, it is a lot more solid.

00:04:50.790 --> 00:04:54.750
So if I had more time and pretty more
inclination because I'm freezing cold

00:04:54.750 --> 00:04:58.790
here, I pretty could get away of it, but
it's a last resort, and remember, if you

00:04:58.790 --> 00:05:02.330
do do it this way, be very very careful on
the way home, particularly when you're

00:05:02.330 --> 00:05:05.080
going around corners. It's not
going to have the same strength.

00:05:05.080 --> 00:05:08.580
There's a likelihood that the tire might
roll off the rims, so just be very careful

00:05:08.580 --> 00:05:12.128
on your way home. But if you do get
away with it, let us know in the comment

